 grip needed to walk on rough terrain without slipping."}, {"version": "sun", "text": "The mud stuck to Mudbray\u2019s hooves enhances its grip and its powerful running gait."}, {"version": "sword", "text": "Loads weighing up to 50 times as much as its own body weight pose no issue for this Pok\u00e9mon. It\u2019s skilled at making use of mud."}, {"version": "ultra-moon", "text": "Possessing mighty power, Mudbray can be loaded with 50 times its own body weight and will be totally fine."}, {"version": "ultra-sun", "text": "It loves playing in the mud. If it isn\u2019t showered with mud on a daily basis, it gets stressed out and stops listening to its Trainer."}], "entryGameVersions": ["moon", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun"], "moveGameGroups": ["scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "mudbray"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "mudsdale"}]}